Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}二人が愛した世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:25.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}だから遠くまで歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}ほかの誰も　僕や君になれるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:44.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}失った輝きを二人で取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}俯いてる顔をあげた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:50.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}信じてみたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:52.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不安ごと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:57.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}確かなことはなにもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}まだ冷えてゆく体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}嘘を一つ重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:07.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}自分から逃げたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:11.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}一人じゃないから今
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:16.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}もっと遠くまで歩き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:20.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}失うことも怖くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}染み付いた影がまた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:28.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}胸の内側を苦しめるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:39.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}これからは平気笑顔が溢れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}屹立于我们热爱的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:25.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}迈向遥远的彼方不再是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}无人能取代你我在彼此心中的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:44.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}让我们一起夺回失去的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}告别灰心丧气的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:50.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}试着再相信一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:52.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}连同不安一起紧紧相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:57.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}一切都是这么忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:01.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}仍在逐渐变冷的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}陷入谎言的无限轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:07.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不想再自我逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.95,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:11.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不再孤身一人的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:16.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}能够迈向地平线的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:20.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}不再害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:28.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}依旧令内心痛苦难耐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:39.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}但是未来的我一定能重拾失去的笑容
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不赶紧的话  就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的关心  不过今天是周日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在已经是早上10点左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有课  现在也已经迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  no  看我都做了什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  回去再睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉最近满大小姐傻事越做越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该说她们是变得开朗了  还是不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这果然是因为那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐也很黏着他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳也很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从风见先生来到这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家变得开朗起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这明明是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却无法坦率地高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是也改变一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改变这种事能被允许吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看电视吧  电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在浴缸里连100都无法数到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有忍耐力的孩子越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以说是「宽松教育」的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又不是我喜欢才对自己宽松的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要成为在浴缸里能数到1万的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能忍的女人事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2404
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2405
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2406
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2407
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2410
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸  饭菜要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道小幸的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去准备些新的冰块才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我房间的冰箱里有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜  来帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我能叫您小雄吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸  抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了  真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快考试了他不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我拿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要好好复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的内容会在考试里出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这个世界上会有考试这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试啊  考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话  让考试消失也办的到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别说这种荒谬的事让小幸困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是真的想她那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后她就一直把自己关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也一直是电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满说傻话已经是司空见惯的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照往常的话  幸也应该理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管的话  我想也不会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之前发生过浴室那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我之后找幸谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给风见君办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前有没有听说过仅仅想让考试消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女生便在学校里放了火这个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚  发生过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事  我就不问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一件事希望你能明确地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会让小岭同学做出什么危险的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生那样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会全力安排好  让幸和你们免受危害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你之前的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  到时希望你能助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须成为好孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得告诉小岭同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没法阻止考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果阿幸还是没来上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天好像很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以放心了  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被雄二叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被风见先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想偷跑也是白费力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您误会了  我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  叫我们过来的哥哥自己却不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要不先离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是雄二还没过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…都这么晚了  不太安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求各位了  快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身子还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午都请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有事瞒着我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟平时没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太奇怪了  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是快回宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  你们快给我到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  各位也快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来所有人都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在暑假前  整顿一下宿舍的纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管是突然召集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位依然全部到场让我感到很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事在宿舍做不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  所有人都回宿舍去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我收拾一下再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是太莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给风见我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  到底是搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之后肯定会有少儿不宜的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸药…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经改造成倒计为0就停止运行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以外行的水准来说这炸弹相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像吓唬得有点过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了那个城市的  那个公园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了啊  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您终于想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到周围打听了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸运碰到了你的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听他说你的父母遭遇了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家经营着一个小工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然生活艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父母都非常疼爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可一旦工作繁忙起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就没空陪着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟风见先生相遇正好就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从您那寂寞的表情中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了跟自己相似的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您在一起玩耍的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我忘记了寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  您渐渐地不再去那个公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那一天  10岁的生日到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  今天是你的生日  我们就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些日子以来让你那么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定今天一整天都陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想庆祝生日你们两个自己庆祝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是在乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原谅他们俩用寂寞两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就概括了我忍受了那么久的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一个人在公园冷静下来后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才发觉到自己说的话是那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈成了植物人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的任性  才让他们遭遇事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必须做个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能乖乖听话的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  我在那个城市也想起了一些自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你有听到我叫你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时有一点家庭烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情很低落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过多亏了你任性地带我疯玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我心情好了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性有时也能救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的师父也说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她说一句任性话都不懂说  太老实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让人看着就觉得心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母肯定也在你一直忍受着的痛苦里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想着孩子和工作究竟哪个重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终他们得出了还是要把孩子放在第一的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你父母所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的任性有时也会让父母感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你再多任性一点也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人努力到现在真是辛苦你了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师父还说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不报才可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:19:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那时的我被幸所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那这次当是给她报恩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在把你制作的炸药引爆销毁证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被其他人发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经准备好了对策  把耳朵捂住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是为掩盖爆炸声而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看看烟花也挺不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那次事故之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一次都没去探望过看你母亲对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为母亲肯定憎恨着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可那天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这钥匙是你叔叔给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你10岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你的未来是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你可以永远保持笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是将你的名字起为幸的我们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱对你来说可能还有点难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用这句话表达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你生为我们的孩子  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这话该我说才对  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说虽然不明显
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实有着恢复的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想以后多去探望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以任性一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能请您拥抱我一分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一分钟就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只要这点就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  世界树的种子I